{
  "texts": [
    "• Conducting a validity assessment on the AI output and recommendations [44].",
    "• Allowing users to directly interact with AI-enabled systems to construct comprehensive mental models about the entire AI pipeline to help them understand the output and recommendations [37].",
    "• Supporting users by calibrating their confidence in a hypothesis based on available evidence [60].",
    "• Comparing AI output and recommendations with not only the domain experts' and users' knowledge and experience, but also other similar AI-enabled systems, and peers [39].stakeholder understanding of ethical implications [38,56,61].",
    "Such teamwork was proven to make the process of developing an AI-enabled system fairer because AI experts, users, and other stakeholders with limited technical knowledge were all involved and well-informed in making each decision [38]."
  ]
}